    },
  },
  {
    title: { en: 'Biomedical data', zh: '生物医学数据' },
    body: {
      en: 'Endoscopic image analysis, surgical scene understanding, medical information extraction, GWAS and pharmacogenomic analysis.',
      zh: '内窥镜图像分析、手术场景理解、医学信息抽取、GWAS 与药物基因组学分析。',
    },
  },
  {
