    body: {
      en: 'Python (proficient), R (proficient), C++ (basic). Git, Blender, Unity.',
      zh: 'Python（熟练）、R（熟练）、C++（基础）。Git、Blender、Unity。',
    },
  },
  {
    title: { en: 'Evaluation & methodology', zh: '评估与方法论' },
    body: {
      en: 'Designing evaluation frameworks for LLM and CV outputs — measuring fine-grained reliability under real-world variability, not just benchmark accuracy. Statistical rigor carried over from GWAS and pharmacogenomic analysis.',
      zh: '设计面向大模型与计算机视觉输出的评估框架——细粒度衡量真实场景变异性下的可靠性，而不只是 benchmark 上的准确率。统计严谨性延续自 GWAS 与药物基因组学分析的训练。',
